title: crown of deep winter
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

This icy crown grants the wearer resistance to cold damage. In addition, you may cast the following spells: [[cone of cold]], [[fire shield]] (chill shield only), [[investiture of ice]]. If you already know any of these spells, casting them using this crown costs one less [[stress]] than normal.